- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with an emotion analysis task and proposes a model to predict emotions in dialogues.
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper mentions that the code will be available in the Github page.
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is also a less likely category, but the paper deals with emotions in colloquial dialogues, which could be related to the societal impact of technology.
